1. *Vas* je čekao danima. (You were waited for days.) 
2. Primio je *vaš* poziv. (He accepted your invitation.)
3. Hvala *vama* na podršci. (Thank you for your support.)
4. *Vas* je obavestio o promeni. (He informed you of the change.) 
5. On je poštovao *vaše* odluke. (He respected your decisions.) 
6. Ona je slala *vaše* poruke. (She was sending your messages.)